---
import Section from "~/components/Section.astro";
import Container from "~/components/Container.astro";
import CTA from "~/components/landing/CTA.astro";
---

<Section id="inicio" class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 -z-10 h-[32rem] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(251,146,60,0.18),transparent_45%),radial-gradient(circle_at_85%_20%,rgba(244,114,182,0.14),transparent_28%)]"></div>
  <Container class:list="relative z-10 !pt-10 !pb-20 md:!pt-16 lg:!pt-20 lg:!pb-24">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.08fr_.92fr] lg:items-center lg:gap-14">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-orange-200 bg-white/80 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-orange-700 shadow-sm md:text-sm">Escuela de música en Valencia</p>
        <h1 class="mt-6 max-w-xl">La Casita Musical Kid Pam Pum</h1>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-fuchsia-700 md:text-2xl">Un espacio donde crear, jugar y disfrutar forman parte de una sola experiencia.</p>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-base text-slate-600 md:text-xl">Aquí aprenderás música de forma natural, inmersiva y divertida, como cuando aprendes un nuevo idioma viviendo en ese país.</p>

        <div class="mt-9 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap">
          <CTA href="/#clases" label="Ver clases" class="sm:min-w-[180px]" />
          <CTA href="/#contacto" label="Inscribirme" variant="outline" class="sm:min-w-[180px]" />
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 grid max-w-xl grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Niños</p>
            <p class="mt-1">Grupos por edad</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Adultos</p>
            <p class="mt-1">Todos los niveles</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/80 bg-white/70 px-4 py-3 shadow-sm sm:col-span-1">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Colegios</p>
            <p class="mt-1">Propuesta educativa</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-xl">
        <div class="absolute -left-6 top-8 h-24 w-24 rounded-3xl bg-orange-300/60 blur-2xl md:-left-10"></div>
        <div class="absolute -right-8 bottom-2 h-32 w-32 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-300/50 blur-2xl"></div>

        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-white/80 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.95)_0%,rgba(255,249,242,0.96)_100%)] p-5 shadow-[0_24px_70px_rgba(15,23,42,0.11)] md:p-8">
          <div class="rounded-[1.6rem] bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#fff1e7_0%,#fff8f5_50%,#fdf2f8_100%)] p-5 md:p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-orange-700">Experiencia musical</p>
                <p class="mt-2 font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 md:text-3xl">Aprender haciendo</p>
              </div>
              <div class="grid h-12 w-12 place-content-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 text-orange-500 shadow-sm">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-6">
                  <path d="M19 2a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v11.382a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-2-3.163V7.618l-8 2.286v8.478a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-2-3.163V5.857a1 1 0 0 1 .725-.961l10-2.857A1 1 0 0 1 19 2Z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-orange-700">Creatividad activa</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6">Improvisación, ritmo y juego musical desde el primer día.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-fuchsia-700">Aprendizaje inmersivo</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6">Escucha, práctica y expresión con acompañamiento cercano.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="sm:col-span-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/70 bg-white/70 p-4 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-700">Ambiente cálido y profesional</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6">Grupos por edades, propuestas para todos los niveles y conexión real con la música.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-slate-600 md:text-sm md:tracking-[0.12em]">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">Ritmo</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">Melodía</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">Instrumentos</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-2 shadow-sm">Comunidad</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-6 bottom-0 h-10 rounded-full bg-orange-200/30 blur-2xl"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
